A fence
stolen at the Soweto Country Club was recovered in a sting operation on
Thursday.The City of
Joburg’s Group Forensic and Investigation Service (GFIS) led the sting
operation with the Joburg Metro Police Department (JMPD) and the South African
Police Service.The fence,
worth R80 000, was recovered from a block of flats in Eldorado Park, south of
